---
// Standalone pitch deck — no site layout
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SimpleScheduleAI — Pitch Deck</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <style>
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      :root {
        --bg: #07071a;
        --surface: #0e0e26;
        --border: rgba(99, 120, 255, 0.18);
        --accent: #5c7cfa;
        --accent2: #a78bfa;
        --green: #34d399;
        --text: #eef0ff;
        --muted: #8892c4;
        --slide-w: 1280px;
        --slide-h: 720px;
      }

      html,
      body {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: #03030f;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        overflow: hidden;
        user-select: none;
      }

      /* ── Viewport scaler ── */
      #scaler {
        position: fixed;
        inset: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      #deck {
        position: relative;
        width: var(--slide-w);
        height: var(--slide-h);
        transform-origin: center center;
      }

      /* ── Slides ── */
      .slide {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 64px 80px;
        background: var(--bg);
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        transition: opacity 0.45s ease;
      }
      .slide.active {
        opacity: 1;
        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      /* grid noise texture overlay */
      .slide::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image:
          radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.07) 0%, transparent 50%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.07) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      /* ── Common elements ── */
      .tag {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .tag .dot {
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--accent);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 72px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 52px;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.1;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }
      h3 {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .accent {
        color: var(--accent);
      }
      .accent2 {
        color: var(--accent2);
      }
      .green {
        color: var(--green);
      }

      .sub {
        font-size: 22px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-top: 20px;
        max-width: 800px;
      }

      .divider {
        width: 60px;
        height: 4px;
        border-radius: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
        margin: 28px 0;
      }

      /* card */
      .card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 28px 32px;
      }

      /* number stat */
      .stat-num {
        font-size: 64px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }
      .stat-label {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-top: 4px;
      }

      /* grid layouts */
      .grid-2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
      }
      .grid-3 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 20px;
      }
      .grid-4 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 16px;
      }

      /* list */
      .check-list {
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 14px;
      }
      .check-list li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 14px;
        font-size: 20px;
        color: var(--text);
        line-height: 1.4;
      }
      .check-list li .icon {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        margin-top: 2px;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.15);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 13px;
      }

      /* step */
      .step-num {
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .step-title {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .step-desc {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      /* comparison row */
      .vs-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 60px 1fr;
        gap: 0;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .vs-col {
        padding: 20px 28px;
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      .vs-col.left {
        border-radius: 16px 0 0 16px;
      }
      .vs-col.right {
        border-radius: 0 16px 16px 0;
        border-left: none;
        background: rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.08);
        border-color: rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.35);
      }
      .vs-badge {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        color: var(--muted);
        background: var(--bg);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        height: 100%;
      }
      .vs-label {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--muted);
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .vs-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .vs-x {
        color: #f87171;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .vs-check {
        color: var(--green);
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      /* pill */
      .pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        padding: 6px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        background: rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.12);
        border: 1px solid rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.3);
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      /* nav bar */
      #nav {
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 32px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 16px;
        background: rgba(14, 14, 38, 0.9);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        z-index: 100;
      }
      #nav button {
        background: none;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 18px;
        padding: 4px 8px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: color 0.2s;
      }
      #nav button:hover {
        color: var(--text);
      }
      #counter {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--muted);
        min-width: 50px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .progress-dots {
        display: flex;
        gap: 6px;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .dot-nav {
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--border);
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        padding: 0;
        transition: all 0.25s;
      }
      .dot-nav.active {
        background: var(--accent);
        width: 20px;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }

      /* slide-specific tweaks */
      #s1 {
        justify-content: center;
      }
      #s1 h1 {
        font-size: 64px;
      }
      #s1 .logo-mark {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
      }
      #s1 .logo-mark::before {
        content: '';
        display: block;
        width: 32px;
        height: 2px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      }
      #s1 .byline {
        margin-top: 52px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 32px;
      }
      #s1 .byline-name {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      #s1 .byline-name strong {
        color: var(--text);
      }

      #s2 .big-pain {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-top: 36px;
      }
      #s2 .pain-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 28px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }
      #s2 .pain-icon {
        font-size: 28px;
      }
      #s2 .pain-title {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      #s2 .pain-body {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      /* slide 7 — compact 2×2 grid to stay within 592px */
      #s7 h2 {
        font-size: 42px;
      }
      #s7 .divider {
        margin: 16px 0;
      }
      #s7 .grid-2 {
        margin-top: 8px !important;
        gap: 14px !important;
      }
      #s7 .card {
        padding: 20px 24px;
      }
      #s7 .card p {
        font-size: 14px !important;
        margin-top: 8px !important;
      }

      /* slide 8 — compact to prevent overflow */
      #s8 h2 {
        font-size: 38px;
      }
      #s8 .divider {
        margin: 14px 0;
      }
      #s8 .card {
        padding: 18px 22px;
      }
      #s8 .check-list {
        gap: 7px !important;
      }
      #s8 .check-list li {
        font-size: 15px !important;
      }
      #s8 .check-list li .icon {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        font-size: 11px;
      }

      #s9 {
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }
      #s9 .cta-card {
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.4);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 52px 72px;
        margin-top: 40px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
      }
      #s9 .email-link {
        font-size: 22px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.4);
        padding-bottom: 2px;
      }
      #s9 .url {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      /* glow ring on title */
      .glow-ring {
        position: absolute;
        right: 80px;
        top: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
        width: 320px;
        height: 320px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
        border: 1px solid rgba(92, 124, 250, 0.15);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }
      .glow-ring .ring-stat {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: var(--accent);
      }
      .glow-ring .ring-label {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.4;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="scaler">
      <div id="deck">
        <!-- ── SLIDE 1: Title ── -->
        <section class="slide active" id="s1">
          <div class="logo-mark">SimpleScheduleAI</div>
          <h1>
            Nurse Scheduling<br />for <span class="accent">Critical Access</span><br />Hospitals — <span class="accent2"
              >Solved.</span
            >
          </h1>
          <p class="sub">
            An AI-powered managed service that eliminates manual scheduling<br />so CAH administrators can focus on
            running their hospital.
          </p>
          <div class="byline">
            <div class="byline-name"><strong>Pradeep Pandey</strong> · Founder</div>
            <div class="pill">Texas · 2024</div>
            <div class="pill">Free 60-Day Pilot Open</div>
          </div>
          <div class="glow-ring">
            <div class="ring-stat">≤25</div>
            <div class="ring-label">beds.<br />Underserved<br />by every tool<br />on the market.</div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ── SLIDE 2: Problem ── -->
        <section class="slide" id="s2">
          <div class="tag"><span class="dot"></span>The Problem</div>
          <h2>CAH Nurse Managers<br />are buried in <span class="accent">scheduling.</span></h2>
          <div class="big-pain">
            <div class="pain-card">
              <div class="pain-icon">🕐</div>
              <div class="pain-title">8–12 hrs/week — gone</div>
              <div class="pain-body">
                Nurse managers spend a full day each week juggling spreadsheets, tracking availability, and manually
                enforcing shift rules.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-card">
              <div class="pain-icon">⚠️</div>
              <div class="pain-title">Rules get violated</div>
              <div class="pain-body">
                Texas overtime rules, CMS PBJ reporting, charge nurse ratios — manual scheduling misses constraints that
                trigger compliance risk.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="pain-card">
              <div class="pain-icon">📞</div>
              <div class="pain-title">Callouts = chaos</div>
              <div class="pain-body">
                A single unexpected callout cascades into hours of calls, texts, and manual rescheduling — every time,
                every shift.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ── SLIDE 3: Market ── -->
        <section class="slide" id="s3">
          <div class="tag"><span class="dot"></span>The Market</div>
          <h2>A large, <span class="accent">underserved</span> segment<br />with no good options.</h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <div class="grid-3" style="margin-top: 12px;">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="stat-num">1,300+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Critical Access Hospitals in the U.S.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="stat-num">80+</div>
              <div class="stat-label">CAHs in Texas alone — our initial market</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="stat-num">0</div>
              <div class="stat-label">
                Scheduling tools built <em>for</em> CAHs — not adapted from large health systems
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="sub" style="margin-top: 28px; font-size: 18px;">
            Enterprise tools (QGenda, UKG) require IT teams CAHs don't have.<br />Generic apps (Aladtec, ShiftWizard)
            weren't designed for CAH compliance rules.<br /><strong style="color: var(--text);"
              >Nobody is solving this the right way.</strong
            >
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- ── SLIDE 4: Solution ── -->
        <section class="slide" id="s4">
          <div class="tag"><span class="dot"></span>Our Solution</div>
          <h2>
            We schedule <span class="accent">your nurses.</span><br />You approve. <span class="accent2">Done.</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 8px; align-items: start;">
            <div>
              <ul class="check-list">
                <li>
                  <span class="icon">✓</span>AI-generated schedules built around your unit's rules — charge ratios,
                  skill mix, overtime limits
                </li>
                <li>
                  <span class="icon">✓</span>Three draft options every cycle: balanced coverage, fairness-optimized, and
                  cost-optimized
                </li>
                <li>
                  <span class="icon">✓</span>Real-time callout management — AI ranks the top 3 replacements with
                  reasoning, one-click approval
                </li>
                <li>
                  <span class="icon">✓</span>Schedules delivered as PDF and Excel. No new software for nurses to learn.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card" style="background: rgba(92,124,250,0.06); border-color: rgba(92,124,250,0.3);">
              <p
                style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;"
              >
                The core insight
              </p>
              <p style="font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text);">
                "CAH administrators don't have time to learn new software. They need the <span class="accent"
                  >schedule done</span
                > — and they need it <span class="accent">right.</span>"
              </p>
              <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
                <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted);">
                  This is why we're a <strong style="color: var(--text);">managed service</strong>, not another
                  scheduling app.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ── SLIDE 5: How It Works ── -->
        <section class="slide" id="s5">
          <div class="tag"><span class="dot"></span>How It Works</div>
          <h2>Live in <span class="accent">under 2 weeks.</span><br />Zero IT involvement.</h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <div class="grid-4" style="margin-top: 16px;">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="step-num">STEP 01</div>
              <div class="step-title">Upload Roster</div>
              <div class="step-desc">
                Export your nurse list from HR or EHR into Excel. Upload it to SimpleScheduleAI.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="step-num">STEP 02</div>
              <div class="step-title">Configure Rules</div>
              <div class="step-desc">
                We configure your shift structure, Texas overtime constraints, and facility-specific requirements.
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="step-num">STEP 03</div>
              <div class="step-title">Review Drafts</div>
              <div class="step-desc">AI generates 3 schedule options. You review, provide feedback, approve.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="step-num">STEP 04</div>
              <div class="step-title">Go Live</div>
              <div class="step-desc">
                Schedules published and distributed. Callout replacements handled automatically going forward.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 28px; display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <div class="pill">No IT project</div>
            <div class="pill">No staff training</div>
            <div class="pill">Automated audit trail</div>
            <div class="pill">Texas overtime compliance</div>
            <div class="pill">CMS PBJ reporting ready</div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ── SLIDE 6: Why We Win ── -->
        <section class="slide" id="s6">
          <div class="tag"><span class="dot"></span>Competitive Advantage</div>
          <h2>Managed service vs. <span class="accent2">scheduling software.</span></h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <div class="vs-row" style="margin-top: 16px;">
            <div class="vs-col left">
              <div class="vs-label">Legacy Software Tools</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-x">✗</span> Require IT setup and ongoing maintenance</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-x">✗</span> Staff must log in and learn the tool</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-x">✗</span> Built for large health systems, not CAHs</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-x">✗</span> Admin still builds the schedule manually</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-x">✗</span> No Texas-specific compliance rules</div>
            </div>
            <div class="vs-badge">VS</div>
            <div class="vs-col right">
              <div class="vs-label" style="color: var(--accent);">SimpleScheduleAI</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-check">✓</span> Zero IT — live in under 2 weeks</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-check">✓</span> Nurses never touch software</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-check">✓</span> Purpose-built for CAHs (≤25 beds)</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-check">✓</span> We do the scheduling — you approve</div>
              <div class="vs-item"><span class="vs-check">✓</span> Texas overtime + CMS PBJ built in</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ── SLIDE 7: Differentiators ── -->
        <section class="slide" id="s7">
          <div class="tag"><span class="dot"></span>Why SimpleScheduleAI</div>
          <h2>Built for the <span class="accent">one problem</span><br />CAHs actually have.</h2>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 12px; gap: 20px;">
            <div class="card">
              <h3 style="font-size: 20px;">🧠 AI-Ranked Callout Replacement</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6;">
                When a nurse calls out, the system surfaces the top 3 replacements — with reasoning for each. One-click
                approval. No phone chain.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3 style="font-size: 20px;">📋 Texas Compliance, Built In</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6;">
                Overtime rules, CMS PBJ staffing data, and audit trail logging are enforced automatically — not
                something the admin has to track manually.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3 style="font-size: 20px;">⚖️ Three Schedule Philosophies</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6;">
                Every cycle delivers balanced coverage, fairness-optimized, and cost-optimized drafts. Administrators
                choose — AI executes.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <h3 style="font-size: 20px;">🚀 No Adoption Risk</h3>
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.6;">
                Schedules arrive as Excel and PDF. Staff receive their schedules exactly as before. Zero change
                management required.
              </p>
